{"tid":56520,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"（貓奴）朋友主人病危","createTime":"2016-12-27T09:53:43.000Z","updateTime":"2016-12-27T12:19:05.000Z","uid":44579,"like":2,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"638f3d1e7577137d56bfa77d12e0978a073bd5e3","tid":56520,"uid":44579,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-27T09:53:43.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://holland.pk/sati73m9\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fholland.pk%2Fsati73m9&h=cc439a0b&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n醫生話肥仔急需輸血，請各位share<br />\n<br />\n緊急召集所有黃唐，英短，金吉拉過黎check / 幫手<br />\n<br />\n現hct 跌到得番13.7% , B 型血<br />\n<br />\n肥仔急需輸血，請幫忙及儘快聯絡6733 5227"},{"pid":"c2239fc4eebd8e0d515fda02ed4d520e25dece1f","tid":56520,"uid":44579,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-27T09:57:25.000Z","msg":"(2016-12-27 11:31)<br />\n<br />\n聯絡電話：67335227<br />\n<br />\n各位好, 我家貓- 肥仔 , 5歲, 英短。因為12月25號全日無食野/大小2便, 12月26日發現有異樣即刻帶佢睇醫生, 驗血報告顯示最大問題係HCT 得16.5%。貧血, 成因相信係失血性貧血, 傳染性貧血, 同俾醫生檢查時按完膀肛即賴橙紅色血水尿, 相信係同膀肛同尿道發炎。<br />\n<br />\n肥仔尋晚係診所過夜, 需要聞氧同食抗身素, (醫生表示要睇陣間12月27日中午2-3點再驗血睇HCT 有無上升番, 但如果HCT趺落12%, 情況會好危急同立刻需要輸血)<br />\n<br />\n暫時未知血型, 但都安排下午會驗埋, 會再更新血型及下午資料。<br />\n<br />\n唔該晒各位！"},{"pid":"659e33fb3e612a3c20ab0b9dc6408f75d0f4548d","tid":56520,"uid":44579,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-27T10:14:59.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"de524cfb2d9954424a0772edade766db35e88389","tid":56520,"uid":12158,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-27T10:17:27.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 幫你推"},{"pid":"67533f1b2ab1a5e6958cb221bda9f8d9311fca2f","tid":56520,"uid":61083,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-27T10:23:16.000Z","msg":"推<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6ec37bfc24699e1a9a0ec5f8595018e293a186a3","tid":56520,"uid":58556,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"cited